on, the nature of romanticism and classicism, and the ever-perplexing question of composer versus interpreter.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2020) 7aMUSIC / Musical Instruments / Piano & Keyboard.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press eBook Package Archivez978311053801440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300147025423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300147025.jpg  a978-3-11-053801-4  Yale University Press eBook Package Archive  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles